OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FBy Emily Youlton, ITV News Senior
OL,7,FPolitics Producer
OL,9,FAndy Burnham seems poised to succeed
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer after the prime
OL,11,Fminister announced his resignation on
OL,12,FMonday, and is widely considered the
OL,13,Ffrontrunner for the role.
OL,15,FJust days ago, the former Mayor of
OL,16,FGreater Manchester won a crucial by-
OL,17,Felection in Makerfield, which had been
OL,18,Ftriggered with the sole purpose of
OL,19,Fallowing him to run for the leadership
OL,20,Fas a sitting member of parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FBurnham had not even taken his seat in
OL,7,Fparliament before crushing pressure
OL,8,Fwithin the party prompted Starmer's
OL,9,Fresignation. Only minutes after, he
OL,10,Fconfirmed on social media that he
OL,11,Fwould seek the top job.
OL,13,FWhile the 'King of the North' already
OL,14,Fset out several policy ideas during
OL,15,Fhis by-election campaign, it is not
OL,16,Fyet clear what his exact plans are for
OL,17,FWestminster.
OL,19,FHere, ITV News looks at some of the
OL,20,Fchanges Burnham may try to implement
OL,21,Fif he enters Downing Street.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FTaking Manchesterism to Westminster
OL,8,FOn Monday morning, Labour group
OL,9,FMainstream, which works closely with
OL,10,FBurnham, published a report called The
OL,11,FProductive State: A Framework for
OL,12,FManchesterism.
OL,14,FIt sets out how they believe he can
OL,15,Fscale up the policies of his time as
OL,16,FMayor to fit the whole of the UK,
OL,17,Fcalling for things like "public
OL,18,Fownership, democratic reform, and
OL,19,Fbetter taxation of wealth".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FIt also focuses on "public control of
OL,7,Fessentials" to improve the lives of
OL,8,Fworking people.
OL,10,FCost of Living
OL,12,FThe report from Burnham's team
OL,13,Fsuggests that almost two-thirds of the
OL,14,Fpublic believe the cost-of-living
OL,15,Fcrisis will never end.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FIn his victory speech in Makerfield on
OL,7,FFriday, he said: "We do need to bring
OL,8,Fdown water bills, energy bills, rail
OL,9,Ffares, just as we brought down bus
OL,10,Ffares in Greater Manchester, to make
OL,11,Flife more affordable for people".
OL,13,FThe framework set out by Burnham
OL,14,Fsupporters blames austerity under the
OL,15,FConservatives, Brexit, and general
OL,16,Fprivatisation as causing factors of
OL,17,Fthe crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FTo resolve this, the plan suggests
OL,7,Fpublic ownership could be the
OL,8,Fsolution, by bringing essential
OL,9,Findustries back so that prices can be
OL,10,Fcapped and regulated by a public body,
OL,11,Fand drive down prices.
OL,13,FPublic Ownership
OL,15,FBurnham has consistently said that
OL,16,Fsectors like energy, water, housing
OL,17,Fand transport should be brought under
OL,18,Fpublic control.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FHe wants to reduce privatisation and
OL,7,Fintroduce more public ownership as a
OL,8,Fway to tackle the cost of living and
OL,9,Fbring bills down.
OL,11,FStarmer's government has already begun
OL,12,Fre-nationalisation, creating GB Energy
OL,13,Fand bringing rail services under
OL,14,Fpublic control through Great British
OL,15,FRail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FA Burnham government could continue
OL,7,Fthis plan, especially as Louise Haigh,
OL,8,Fwho ran Burnham's campaign in
OL,9,FMakerfield, instigated this policy
OL,10,Fwhen she was transport secretary under
OL,11,FStarmer.
OL,13,FOne of Burnham's biggest successes in
OL,14,FManchester was the Bee Network, a
OL,15,Fpublicly regulated transport system
OL,16,Frun by private operators with #2 bus
OL,17,Ffares.
OL,19,FBurnham is also keen to continue the
OL,20,Fdevolution to regions and cities to
OL,21,Fmanage their own transport and housing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FHe has repeatedly advocated for
OL,7,Fbringing water "back under stronger
OL,8,Fpublic control" and has said companies
OL,9,Flike Thames Water should be in public
OL,10,Fownership.
OL,12,FSocial Care
OL,14,FSince his time as a health minister
OL,15,Funder Tony Blair in 2006-7 and then
OL,16,Fhealth secretary under Gordon Brown in
OL,17,F2009-10, Burnham has been a supporter
OL,18,Fof social care reform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FOne of his suggestions has been to
OL,7,Freplace inheritance tax with a
OL,8,F"national care levy" which he
OL,9,Fpreviously said would mean that care
OL,10,F"is provided for free".
OL,12,FHe was questioned on these commitments
OL,13,Fduring the by-election and said he did
OL,14,Fnot "resile" from his previous stance.
OL,16,FIt's unclear how much this tax change
OL,17,Fwould actually raise, with some
OL,18,Festimates suggesting that NHS-style
OL,19,Fmodel of universal care could cost
OL,20,Faround #17 billion in extra funding by
OL,21,F2035.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FCouncil Housing
OL,13,FHousing is thought to be on the list
OL,14,Fof main priorities for Burnham.
OL,16,FWhen launching his campaign, Burnham
OL,17,Fsaid he wanted "the biggest programme
OL,18,Fof council house building since the
OL,19,FSecond World War."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FBurnham said this could be funded by
OL,7,Fdiverting the existing affordable
OL,8,Fhousing programme of #39 billion to
OL,9,Fsocial rent homes.
OL,11,FBurnham has long been a campaigner for
OL,12,Fbringing transport back into public
OL,13,Fownership, supported further by the
OL,14,Fpublication of the Manchesterism
OL,15,Fpolicy document, which calls for a
OL,16,Froll-out of re-nationalisation across
OL,17,Fthe country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FThe "King of the North" has also said
OL,7,Fhe wants to resurrect the further leg
OL,8,Fof HS2 between Birmingham and
OL,9,FManchester after the Tories scrapped
OL,10,Fit in 2023.
OL,12,FAt the time of scrapping, it was
OL,13,Festimated that the cost to complete
OL,14,Fwould be #36 billion, which Burnham
OL,15,Fhas suggested could be raised by
OL,16,Fcapturing the rise in land value
OL,17,Faround new stations.
OL,19,FIt is unclear how much money could
OL,20,Factually be raised this way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FHe is also thought to be supportive of
OL,7,Ffunding for Northern Powerhouse Rail,
OL,8,Fwhich Starmer's government putting
OL,9,F#1.1 billion into planning,
OL,10,Fdevelopment and design of the project.
OL,12,FBurnham has said he would stick to the
OL,13,Ffiscal rules set by Chancellor Rachel
OL,14,FReeves and said that the UK needs a
OL,15,Fplan to reduce its debts.
OL,17,FThis suggests he doesn't want to spook
OL,18,Fthe markets by increasing government
OL,19,Fborrowing, at least in the short term.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FBut he has also continued the Labour
OL,7,FParty manifesto pledge not to raise
OL,8,Fincome tax or national insurance for
OL,9,Fworking people.
OL,11,FIn the framework published on Monday,
OL,12,Fit suggests that Burnham would set up
OL,13,Fso-called public corporations,
OL,14,Fallowing them to borrow independently
OL,15,Fagainst those revenues.
OL,17,FSome economists have suggested that
OL,18,FBurnham is likely to lean towards the
OL,19,Fleft of his party on economic
OL,20,Fpolicies, meaning higher taxes and
OL,21,Flooser fiscal rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
