PN,31116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FYoung people
OL,8,FBurnham's education plans are yet to
OL,9,Fbe fleshed out, but he has previously
OL,10,Fsaid that the Education and SEND
OL,11,Fsystems need reform.
OL,13,FHe has also proposed guaranteeing
OL,14,Fevery 16-year-old a work-related
OL,15,Fopportunity, such as a 45-day
OL,16,Fplacement, to tackle youth
OL,17,Funemployment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FThis mirrors Starmer's plans to offer
OL,7,Fwork placements to young people who
OL,8,Fare unemployed and provide businesses
OL,9,Fwith #3,000 incentives to hire those
OL,10,Fwho have been out of work for six
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FHe has also talked about rolling out
OL,14,Ffree bus passes for 16 to 18-year-
OL,15,Folds, replicating a policy already
OL,16,Frolled out in Manchester and London.
OL,18,FBurnham thinks this access to
OL,19,Ftransport helps young people access
OL,20,Feducation and apprenticeships.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FAfter John Healey resigned as
OL,7,FStarmer's defence secretary over a
OL,8,Ffunding row, the question has been
OL,9,Fraised as to whether Burnham would
OL,10,Foffer the 3% GDP that Healey asked for.
OL,12,FBurnham said that alongside the 10-
OL,13,Fyear approach to defence and security,
OL,14,Fthere should be reform of public
OL,15,Finvestment and procurement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782202689
OL,3,CWhat are Andy Burnham's plans for the
OL,4,Ccountry?
OL,6,FOn the question of where this
OL,7,Finvestment would come from, he said he
OL,8,Fwas "not squeamish about saying that
OL,9,Fthe plan would be to reduce the
OL,10,Fwelfare bill" and wanted to get more
OL,11,Fpeople back into work.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
